('P01', 'GLOWING LAB', 20, 30, 'Recommended for ages 6 to 12 years  ', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Science is sweet!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Set the world aglow with peace, happiness and good times! Make yummy candies that actually glow in the dark. Mold fun, glowing gummies and sweet, glowing ice cubes in groovy shapes. Then make a batch of hard candy and watch it glow. A small amount of a safe, natural ingredient &mdash; riboflavin, or vitamin B2 &mdash; causes these candies to glow under the included blacklight flashlight. Learn about the chemistry of glowing materials and pigments, the physics of light and electromagnetic waves, and more science behind these delicious treats. This kit includes all the food ingredients needed for a groovy good time!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-position: inside; list-style-image: inherit; list-style-type: inherit; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Groovy Glowing Candy Lab</span>&nbsp;by Thames &amp; Kosmos is the newest addition to the best-selling candy science line with two new flavors: fruit punch and tropical pineapple.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Make groovy gummies, hard candies and sweet ice cubes that glow in the dark under a black light (UV flashlight included).</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Kit includes all food ingredients, candy mold, and UV flashlight as well as a 16-page manual with instructions and 5 experiments.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">STEM-themed activity kit &ldquo;sneaks&rdquo; in chemistry lessons with mixtures, solutions and luminescence.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Made in the USA.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">FDA compliant with extended shelf life.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Contains small parts! Not suitable for children under age 3 years!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2021-11-04 17:33:01', 10000, 'P01.png', 'C01', 'S01', 'B01'),
('P02', 'FORENSIC LAB', 35, 45, 'Recommended for ages 8 to 14 years', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	Use real techniques to solve impossible cases.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	Use the magic of Chromatography to extract telltale colors from Crime Scene Notes (like DNA analysis). Special indicators spot dangerous ACIDS and ALKALIS. Develop and Lift and Match fingerprints. Trap thieves with glow-in-the-dark inks. Collect Suspect Shoeprints, then compare to your crime scene Footprint Cast. Reveal Secret Messages. Who drove the getaway car? YOU will know using Cloth Fiber Analysis&hellip; and much, much more.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-position: inside; list-style-image: inherit; list-style-type: inherit; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Become a detective! Use real techniques to match fingerprints, analyze DNA, identify fibers, test for poisons, cast footprints and discover secret messages. Set the scene with the crime scene tape!</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		In this kit, children will learn how detectives use forensic science to collect and examine crime scene evidence. Each step in the booklet comes with an illustration to show exactly what needs to be done.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Where&#39;s the secret message? Whose footprints are these? Test your child&#39;s observation skills as they examine the crime scene for evidence!</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Children will learn how to use chromatography to extract evidence from DNA analyses, test acids and alkalis to discover secret writing, examine fingerprint characteristics, collect shoe prints, search the crime scene for hidden messages and so much more!</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		This kit develops logical, analytical and problem-solving skills as children examine evidence to solve cases.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Kit includes a full-color instruction booklet, laboratory tools and high-quality ingredients &mdash; a total of 66 pieces*; some household items are also required, such as paper, scissors, a plate, old shoes and sweaters, a black marker, small mirror or shiny surface and a glass jar.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		UV flashlight requires 3 LR41 button-cell batteries, which are INCLUDED and cannot be replaced.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		WILD! Science products are tested to the highest consumer standards (ASTM and CPSIA).</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Contains small parts!&nbsp;Not suitable for children under age 3 years!</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Parental supervision is recommended.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	*Kit includes: Sodium bicarbonate, citric acid, Plaster of Paris, cornstarch, Universal Indicator strips x 8, beaker, pipette, scoops x 2, tweezers, magnifier, water-based marker pens x 2, cylinder, chromatography paper, UV flashlight and invisible ink marker, spoon, stirring sticks x 5, fingerprint slides, footprint mold wall, tracing paper x 6, cotton balls x 10, cotton buds x 4, ink pad, plain sticky labels, sticky tape, pencil, sample tubes x 5, Crime Scene tape x 3 meters, instruction booklet and safety leaflet.</p>\r\n', '2021-11-04 16:56:37', 9999, 'P02.jpg', 'C01', 'S01', 'B01'),
('P03', 'ROCKET RACERS', 30, 40, 'Recommended for ages 8 to 12 years', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	HIGH-OCTANE HEAD-TO-HEAD ACTION: This&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Fuel &lsquo;N Duel Rocket Racers</span>&nbsp;set includes everything you need to get off to the races! Customize your rocket race cars and make your own awesome racetrack complete with obstacles to blast through!</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	GET READY FOR BLAST OFF! Start your engines, mix your fuel, and blast your race cars to another dimension! If you are looking for a scientific twist on a classic racing game, look no further than this&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Fuel &lsquo;N Duel</span>, where chemistry combines&nbsp;<span class=\"more-content js-more-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">with classic head-to-head racing action!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<span class=\"more-content js-more-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">CUSTOMIZE YOUR RACING CARS, add more weight, swap out wheels and prepare yourself for endless hou