acity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Mix your own fuel, watch the reaction build in the clear fuel chamber &ndash; then get ready for your cars to blast off!</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span class=\"more-content js-more-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Blast-off rocket cars indoors? Yes! With the parent-approved &quot;No Mess Spill-Stoppers&quot;, mess is contained for easy clean-up in seconds.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span class=\"more-content js-more-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Customize your vehicles and test variability! Change the wheels, the weight, and even add a plow or ski.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span class=\"more-content js-more-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Made from kid-friendly, nontoxic materials, this racing toy for kids will ensure your kids play in safety.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span class=\"more-content js-more-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">The&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Fuel &#39;N Duel Rocket Racers</span>&nbsp;set will have your kids exploring STEM while having fun!</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Contains small parts!&nbsp;Not suitable for children under age 3 years!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2021-11-04 16:56:29', 999, 'P03.jpg', 'C01', 'S01', 'B01'),
