('P07', 'MILLENNIUM FALCON', 999, 1199, 'MILLENNIUM FALCON – 75192', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	Make room to display the most famous starship in the galaxy!</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	Welcome to the largest, most detailed LEGO&reg;&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Star&nbsp;Wars&trade;</i>&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Millennium Falcon&trade;</span>&nbsp;model ever created&mdash;in fact, with 7,500 pieces it&rsquo;s one of the biggest LEGO models, period! This amazing LEGO interpretation of Han Solo&rsquo;s unforgettable Corellian freighter has all the details that&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Star&nbsp;Wars</i>&nbsp;fans of any age could wish for, including intricate exterior detailing, upper and lower quad laser cannons, landing legs, lowering boarding ramp and a 4-minifigure cockpit with detachable canopy. Remove individual hull plates to reveal the highly detailed main hold, rear compartment and gunnery station. This amazing model also features interchangeable sensor dishes and crew, so you decide whether to play out classic LEGO&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Star&nbsp;Wars</i>&nbsp;adventures with Han, Leia, Chewbacca and C-3PO, or enter the world of Episode VII and VIII with older Han, Rey, Finn and BB-8!</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-position: inside; list-style-image: inherit; list-style-type: inherit; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Includes four classic crew minifigures: Han Solo&trade;, Chewbacca&trade;, Princess Leia&trade; and C-3PO&trade;.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Also includes three Episode VII/VIII crew minifigures: Older Han Solo, Rey and Finn.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Figures include a BB-8&trade; droid, 2 buildable Porgs and a buildable Mynock.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Exterior features include intricately detailed and removable hull panels, a lowering boarding ramp, concealed blaster cannon, 4-minifigure cockpit with detachable canopy, interchangeable round/rectangular sensor dishes, upper and lower quad laser cannons, and 7 landing legs.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Main hold features a seating area, Dejarik holographic game, combat remote training helmet, engineering station with turning minifigure seat and a doorway build with passageway decoration.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Rear compartment features the engine room with hyperdrive and console, 2 doorways, hidden floor compartment, 2 escape pod hatches, engineering console and an access ladder to the gunnery station.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Gunnery station features a minifigure gunner&rsquo;s seat and detachable hull panel with fully rotating quad laser cannon. An additional quad laser cannon is also mounted on the underside.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Also includes an informational fact plaque.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Features a cockpit canopy element.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Classic crew weapons include Han&rsquo;s blaster pistol and Chewbacca&rsquo;s stud-firing bowcaster.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Assembled&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Millennium Falcon&trade;</span>&nbsp;measures 33 x 22 x 8.25 inches (LxWxH).</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Contains small parts!&nbsp;Not suitable for children under age 3 years.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2021-11-04 17:13:32', 1000, 'P07.jpg', 'C02', 'S02', 'B01'),
('P08', 'DUCATI PANIGALE V4 R', 79, 89, 'DUCATI PANIGALE V4 R – 42107', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">DUCATI PANIGALE V4 R &ndash; 42107</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	Ages 10+ years&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 646 pieces</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	Style, sophistication, performance. Recreate the iconic&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Ducati Panigale V4 R</span>&nbsp;with this LEGO&reg; Technic&trade; set, featuring 2-speed gearbox, front and rear disc brakes and V4-cylinder engine.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	The roar of the engine. The thrill of acceleration. The smooth lean as you take a corner. If you&rsquo;ve ever imagined riding your own Ducati, you&rsquo;ll love building this LEGO&reg; Technic&trade;&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Ducati Panigale V4 R</span>. Discover how the gearbox activates the V4-cylinder engine. See how Ducati achieves a smooth ride with front and rear suspension. Then explore different driving techniques with the 2-speed action.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	With breathtaking looks, this LEGO&reg; Technic&trade;&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Ducati Panigale V4 R</span>&nbsp;captures the spirit and design of the original. It&rsquo;s the first model motorcycle in LEGO Technic history to include a gearbox for exploring different speeds and techniques. Other amazing features include steering, front and rear suspension for realistic movement, plus front and rear disc brakes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	Ducati fans will appreciate the attention-to-detail in this amazing motorcycle replica. A kickstand, exhaust pipe, windshield and dashboard add the little details that make this model toy so true to the full-size version. And of course, the classic red color scheme is sure to quicken the pulse of any Ducati fan.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	As part of the LEGO&reg; Technic&trade; universe, this motorcycle model kit provides an immersive and rewarding building experience. With realistic features, it introduces builders to the world of engineering, as they discover how gear mechanisms work.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-position: inside; list-style-image: inherit; list-style-type: inherit; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		A representation of the famous&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Ducati Panigale V4 R</span>&nbsp;to build, explore and display. LEGO&reg; Technic&trade; fans and motorcycle enthusiasts will love this stunning building challenge.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Build your own&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Ducati Panigale V4 R</span>&nbsp;to gain a unique insight into the features and functions that make up this iconic motorcycle. Also includes a 2-speed gear-box &ndash; a first for LEGO&reg; Technic&trade; motorcycles.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Recreate the thrill of owning a&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Ducati Panigale V4 R</span>, with front and rear suspension for realistic model movement. The classic red color scheme brings the motorcycle to life, with true Italian flair.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Looking for the best gifts for motorbike fans? This is a great choice. It&rsquo;s also a super challenge for LEGO&reg; Technic&trade; fans aged 10+ who will get a thrill from seeing how a motorcycle works.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		This eye-catching model looks stunning on display. Its dimensions have been designed to give a true representation of the real-life model, measuring 12.6 x 3.2 x 6.3 inches (LxWxH).</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		No batteries are needed for this Ducati motorbike toy. Passion, imagination and a desire to discover something new are all you need.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		It&rsquo;s easy to get started with this amazing LEGO&reg; set. Just open the box and you&rsquo;ll find easy-to-follow instructions so building the Ducati toy motorcycle can begin straightaway.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		LEGO&reg; Technic&trade; engineering toys are designed to provide an immersive and rewarding building experience, featuring realistic movement and mechanisms to help kids and adults explore the world of engineering.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		WARNING: Choking Hazard&mdash;Contains small parts!&nbsp;Not suitable for children under age 3 years!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2021-11-04 17:15:07', 1000, 'P08.jpg', 'C02', 'S02', 'B01'),
('P09', 'DINO FAURS', 20, 30, 'Recommended for ages 3 to 9 years', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	The&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Aeromax&nbsp;</em><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Dino-Faurs</span>&nbsp;pull back 4 wheel dinosaur trucks are sure to be a big hit with dinosaur enthusiasts! With the new&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Dino-Faurs</span>&nbsp;you caN have races, pop wheelies, or just go back in time and dream about dinosaur life!&nbsp; Nicely sized at 7&quot;L x 5&quot; H x 4&quot;W, this friction powered pull back T-Rex Truck has high performance 4x4 wheels made from PVC for great traction and detailed realistic spring suspension! Just pull it back and watch it go! FAST!&nbsp; Indoor or Outdoors, even works on carpet.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	Dino-Fours come in two bold color choices, please note your color preference in the drop down menu above -&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\">Red</span>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\">Green</span>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-position: inside; list-style-image: inherit; list-style-type: inherit; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">INCLUDES one dinosaur truck with amazing pull back action that works on most surfaces including carpet.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">INTENDED for ages 3 and up, indoor or outdoor use.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">HIGH QUALITY DURABLE body with state of the art spring suspension for extra fun.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">MOVEABLE mouth and tail, cool teeth, arms, and body detail gives this prehistoric truck a realistic feel. It can also do wheelies for added fun!</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Dino-Faurs measures 7 x 5 x 4&quot;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2021-11-04 17:18:26', 1000, 'P09.jpg', 'C03', 'S03 ', 'B01');
