('P10', 'TRUCK', 130, 150, 'Recommended for ages 4 to 10 years', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	Tow trucks are versatile tools in traffic, regardless of whether they load up broken-down vehicles and take them to the workshop or remove illegally parked vehicles. The MACK&reg; tow truck featuring many functions has now been added to the BRUDER&reg; range.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	The platform can be lowered to recover vehicles. It is also possible to load vehicles using the crane that can be extended and pivoted. In this process, the loading harness, consisting of chains and wheel clamps, enables safe and fast lifting and loading. Wheel chocks and folding outriggers secure the vehicle, and tread tires round off the HGV. The high-detail MACK truck&rsquo;s cab features doors that open and folding mirrors on the cab. The Light &amp; Sound Module is included.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	The new BRUDER roadster features a removable roof and can accommodate any Bworld figure. The BRUDER roadster comes with the new tire changing system for even more fun.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-position: inside; list-style-image: inherit; list-style-type: inherit; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">BRUDER&reg; MACK Granite Tow-Truck with BRUDER Roadster</span>&nbsp;is 1:16 scale.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Cab hood and doors open and include a folding outside mirror.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Windows are made from transparent and shatter-proof plastic.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Tow-Truck body features rubber tires and includes a folding and swiveling hoisting crane and stabilizer legs, and loading platform can be removed.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Crane swivels and extends and includes load handling gear and wheel clamps for loading.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		BRUDER&reg; Roadster is all plastic with removable roof and detachable rubber tires.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Can be used with all Bworld figures, which are&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\">available separately</span>.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Constructed out of fade-resistant, high-quality ABS plastic, with no glue or screws, and rubber tires.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Realistic details and functions encourage imaginative play.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		Great for use indoors and outdoors.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		MACK Granite Tow-Truck measures 21 x 8 x 11 inches (LxWxH).</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\r\n		BRUDER&reg; Roadster measures 11 x 5 x 4 inches (LxWxH).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2021-11-04 17:20:10', 1000, 'P10.jpg', 'C03', 'S03 ', 'B01'),
('P11', 'STEEL WORKS ERECTOR', 30, 40, 'Recommended for ages 8 and up', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	Explore the world of real building with Steel Works, the classic steel construction set. Use the over 350 pieces to build a<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">&nbsp;Steel Works 4x4</span>, with articulated wheels, a working steering wheel, and off-roading tires. Be inspired, challenged and amazed as you explore your creativity and imagination. The durable steel parts let you build and rebuild real toys you can play with. Build something you are proud to display or take it apart and try something new. Each set comes with real steel parts, tools and detailed instructions. Perfect for creative builders!</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: 600; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Product features:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.25s ease-in-out 0s; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-position: inside; list-style-image: inherit; list-style-type: inherit; color: rgb(5, 5, 6); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: opacity 0.2